.:: Puzzle 5x3-Level-6-2::.
There are 3 different favourite beverages: mirinda, soy-milk, tea
The people have 3 different hobbies: cooking, drawing, skydiving
House: futuristic, ranch-style, cape-cod
3 different pets are kept: hamster, horse, pony
The people prefer 3 different types of sport: baseball, cycling, ice-hockey
1. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the right of the person drinking mirinda##5
2. the person who's sport is baseball is between the person drinking tea and the futuristic house##2
3. the person who's sport is ice-hockey is somewhere to the left of the person who's hobby is drawing##5
4. the person who's hobby is skydiving is on the left or right of the person drinking tea##3
5. the owner of the hamster is not the futuristic house##6
6. the person drinking mirinda is in an odd position##4
7. the person who's sport is baseball is somewhere to the left of the person who's sport is cycling##5
8. the person who's hobby is drawing is not the person drinking soy-milk##6
9. the cape-cod house is somewhere to the left of the owner of the pony##5

.:: Answer ::.
|               |     1      |      2      |    3    |
| Beverage      | mirinda    | soy-milk    | tea     |
| Hobby         | cooking    | skydiving   | drawing |
| Movie-Genre   | futuristic    | cape-cod | ranch-style  |
| Pet           | horse      | hamster     | pony    |
| Sport         | ice-hockey | baseball    | cycling |

